| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1162 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 1daa71da-07ea-553b-9b20-00387a2c1ebc"
